  "text": "It is known that this system may present positive resonant frequencies even when the domain is assumed to be of class C 2 (see [CITATION_1] ) or σ is assumed to vanish (see [CITATION_2] ). This means that, for some positive frequencies, the system may have non-trivial solutions of (1) with zero boundary conditions.",
